2026-05-12T03:56:09.2100467Z 13    <!--
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2101123Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2101884Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2102929Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2103687Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2104714Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2105343Z 19        we only request it when the toggle is on.
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2105792Z 20    -->
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2106309Z 21    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_FULL_SCREEN_INTENT" />
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2107185Z 21-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:16:5-81
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2108075Z 21-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:16:22-78
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2108748Z 22    <!--
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2109245Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2109917Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2110540Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2111594Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2112377Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2113205Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2114059Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2114906Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2115724Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-12T03:56:09.2116571Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
